A Neighborhood Cafe Cooking With Love
White Lion Cafe is a unique and family-owned and operated business that has been serving people in Homestead, Florida since 1989. After falling in love with pubs in England, we wanted to have a tea room. At first, we opened an antique shop, but it evolved into the nicest restaurant in town.
What Sets Us Apart
Our team always serves our customers with delightful food that leaves them feeling full and happy. We guarantee great meals every day and maintain a friendly atmosphere.
End Section 2
